metadata.name: INFINITE CHECKS
metadata.description:
These INFINITE CHECKS may or may not be notable.

The INFINITE CHECKS will commit to donate %50 of all NFT mints to the 100 Meals cause, run by @jackbutcher. The 100 Meals cause represents a donation of 100 meals to Feeding America through their network of food banks, making a positive impact on the world. By purchasing an INFINITE CHECKS NFT, collectors not only acquire a unique digital asset, but also make a difference in the lives of those in need. The 100 Meals NFT can be found in the Zora collection at the link: https://zora.co/collections/0x0e33fd2db4f140dca8f65671c40e36f8fd648fff
